org.opentcs.access.queries

Class Query<E extends Query<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opentcs.access.queries.Query<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The actual query class.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueryAvailableScriptFiles, QueryRecoveryStatus, QueryRoutingInfo, QuerySchedulerAllocations, QueryTopologyInfo

    @Availability(value={})
public abstract class Query<E extends Query<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The base class of all results to Kernel queries.

    Note that this class's Availability annotation indicates it is available in no kernel state at all, and since that annotation is inherited, subclasses are required to explicitly define their availability themselves to be usable at runtime.

    See Also:
    Kernel.query(java.lang.Class), Serialized Form
